Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
unplaceAllBlocks(25.10)                                unplaceAllBlocks(25.10)

Name
       unplaceAllBlocks - Unplaces all blocks in the floorplan

Syntax
       unplaceAllBlocks

       [-help]

       Unplaces  all  blocks  in the floorplan. You can use this command after
       importing the design.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs a brief description of the unplaceAllBlocks command.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man unplaceAllBlocks

Related Information
              * Floorplanning the Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

